sentences: Agresta was Bronze Medal winner in the 1989 USA International Harp Competition.
Her debut album, Dream World was released in August 2001.
"The Covers Album" was released on all streaming platforms in May 2019.
The all-original, new age album "Around The Sun" released January, 2020, marking Kirsten's first as composer and winning a Silver Medal at the Global Music Awards.

She made her Carnegie Hall solo recital debut in 1998 in Weill Concert Hall, returning again by popular demand in 1999, and 2002.
